  "description": "《Sunken Dragon》is a retro-style, turn-based Japanese RPG.\n\nFeaturing nostalgic pixel art paired with modernized controls, you’ll guide the protagonist on a journey through this fantastical world. Along the way, you’ll meet comrades who share your goals and form a party to adventure together.\n\nKey Features:• Full controller support\n\n• Up to 4 characters in battle simultaneously\n\n• Deep, branching storylines with extensive hidden content\n\n• Over 20 hours of main-story gameplay\n\n• Vast world map filled with diverse villages and dungeons\n\n• Adjustable movement and battle speeds—set your own pace\n\n• Variety of equipment and extended character progression\n\n• Authentic 8-bit–style graphics and soundtrack",
  "description_short": "This is a retro 8-bit pixel-style RPG. The game features turn-based combat, inviting players to explore the unknown in a fantastical world.",
